'''香港金融博物館'''，為展示[[香港|香港]]金融發展史之博物館，位於香港[[中環|中環]][[交易廣場|交易廣場]]，[[香港交易所|香港交易所]]大堂，由[[香港交易所展覽館|香港交易所展覽館]]改建而成，於2018年2月20日開幕啟用<ref name=mingbao>{{cite|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20180221/s00001/1519143608310/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%82%E6%8F%AD%E5%B9%95-%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%85%E3%80%8C%E5%AD%97%E7%89%86%E3%80%8D%E6%9C%80%E6%90%B6%E7%9C%BC|title=【多圖】香港金融大會堂揭幕　一幅「字牆」最搶眼|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|date=2018-02-21|accessdate=2020-10-27|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108173218/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20180221/s00001/1519143608310/%e3%80%90%e5%a4%9a%e5%9c%96%e3%80%91%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e5%a4%a7%e6%9c%83%e5%a0%82%e6%8f%ad%e5%b9%95-%e4%b8%80%e5%b9%85%e3%80%8c%e5%ad%97%e7%89%86%e3%80%8d%e6%9c%80%e6%90%b6%e7%9c%bc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其展示內容包含中國金融發展史、香港經濟史及港交所歷史等，特色展品有[[抗日戰爭|抗日戰爭]]時期的救國公債、港交所交易員所著之紅衫仔及歷代交易設備等，2019年全年度參觀人次約8000人<ref name=hke2019>{{cite|url=https://www.hkexgroup.com/-/media/HKEX-Group-Site/ssd/Investor-Relations/Regulatory-Reports/documents/2020/c200316csr.pdf|title=2019年企業社會責任報告|page=39|publisher=香港交易所|year=2020|accessdate=2020-10-28|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201185031/https://www.hkexgroup.com/-/media/HKEX-Group-Site/ssd/Investor-Relations/Regulatory-Reports/documents/2020/c200316csr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。。

==爭議==
香港金融博物館開幕當日，貝字牆裝置藝術因呈現許多負面字眼、配色又似骨灰龕<ref name=mingbao/><ref name=hk01>{{cite|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/161576/%E9%97%9C%E5%85%AC%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E8%B2%9D%E5%AD%97%E7%89%86%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E4%BC%BC%E9%AA%A8%E7%81%B0%E9%BE%95-%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE-%E8%B2%AA-%E8%B3%84-%E8%B3%8A-%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC|title=【關公災難】港交所貝字牆被指似骨灰龕　驚現「貪、賄、賊」字眼|publisher=[[hk01|hk01]]|date=2018-02-21|accessdate=2020-10-27|archive-date=2019-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219193521/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/161576/%E9%97%9C%E5%85%AC%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E8%B2%9D%E5%AD%97%E7%89%86%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E4%BC%BC%E9%AA%A8%E7%81%B0%E9%BE%95-%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE-%E8%B2%AA-%E8%B3%84-%E8%B3%8A-%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且博物館甫開幕旋又關閉裝修，而遭大眾質疑<ref name=hkej>{{cite|url=https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/finnews/article/1772585/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E7%94%A9%E8%BD%86+%E9%96%8B%E5%B9%95%E5%8D%B3%E9%96%89%E9%96%80%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE|title=【金融博物館甩轆 開幕即閉門裝修|publisher=[[信報財經新聞|信報財經新聞]]|date=2018-02-21|accessdate=2020-10-27|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105021732/http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/finnews/article/1772585/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E7%94%A9%E8%BD%86+%E9%96%8B%E5%B9%95%E5%8D%B3%E9%96%89%E9%96%80%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


